CTrl+shift+f12 => maximize and minimize editor
Ctrl+tab       => switch between project tabs
shift+shift    => search everthing include code and menu 
ctrl+o         => override Methods
ctrl+i         => implement Methods
ctrl+plus/minus=> collapse and expand the current block of code
ctrl+p         => show parameter of selected method
ctrl+B         => Go to declaration
ctrl+alt+B     => Go to implemention



stop:=> go to super Method

Note : if the file get reddish color it's not added to the repo of gitub

